Let’s be honest, what’s more comforting than a deliciously fresh sandwich? 

That’s why we take Sandwich Day very seriously at TWC. Our sandwiches are made with 24hr slow-fermented focaccia bread, topped with sun-dried tomatoes, fresh garlic, olive oil and rosemary, and served as options for everyone to enjoy!
